      <h1 class="display-4">AIESEC BALL: KEEPSAKE</h1>
      <p>AIESEC Ball is a year-end event celebrating AIESEC in DLSU-M's achievements during the term. This allows us to remember and commmemorate the growth and progress we've made as youth leaders. Let's take part in preserving and remembering those memories by storing them down in this AIESEC Wall!</p>
      <a href="/user/signup" class="btn btn-gradient p-2" style="width: 15%"><strong>Signup now</strong></a>
    </div>
