        <div class="card-body">
          <img src="/photos/post.png" class="mx-2" style="width: 10rem" alt="">
          <h5 class="text-center my-2"><strong>Post</strong></h5>
          <p>Taking note of the guidelines first, feel free to post what you want! There are several tabs where you can post under including Love, Academics, Life, AIESEC, and so on! Just post what’s on your mind, ask for advice, and have fun!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card mx-4 feature-item">
        <div class="card-body">
          <img src="/photos/comment.png" class="card-img" style="width: 10rem;" alt="">
          <h5 class="text-center my-2"><strong>Comment</strong></h5>
          <p>Want to help a fellow AIESECer out? Or maybe you just want to converse with them? This website has the comment feature just for you! Feel free to comment on any of the AIESECers’ post! Have fun!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card mx-4 feature-item">
        <div class="card-body">
          <img src="/photos/reaction.png" class="card-img" style="width: 10rem" alt="">
          <h5 class="text-center my-2"><strong>Heart React</strong></h5>
          <p>Show your love to anyone if you like what they posted by simply clicking the heart button below! Let's spread the love.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
